    ?:  &(=([r.old-yaki ~] p.p.yoki) =(data q.old-yaki))
      ::  [tare] > if no changes, then commits-in-waiting could not have
      ::  changed.
      ::
      ..park
    =/  =yaki
      ?-  -.yoki
        %&  (make-yaki p.p.yoki data now)
        %|  ?>  =(data q.p.yoki)
