    ::
    =?  ..park  &(=(%base syd) !=(old-kel kel))
      =/  desks=(list [=desk =dojo])  ~(tap by dos.rom)
      =^  moves-1  ruf  abet
      =|  moves-2=(list move)
      |-  ^+  ..park
